{"tid":2293199,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行動無對錶 官：紀錄明顯不準","createTime":"2020-11-20T05:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T05:43:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f4e0b0cfda424dcc9d6cc50f7212abb06247ea","tid":2293199,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:38:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/MJQ2WSCR4NCJJJH3DGM45XUSXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FMJQ2WSCR4NCJJJH3DGM45XUSXU%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=fb486dcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FMJQ2WSCR4NCJJJH3DGM45XUSXU%2F&h=70f6bddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/MJQ2WSCR4NCJJJH3DGM45XUSXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n行動無對錶 官：紀錄明顯不準<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lX7fPnIwwLsAiznRF8898IgjFKY=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55KOXHEBGJBFHGM2FDBHQALKTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlX7fPnIwwLsAiznRF8898IgjFKY%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55KOXHEBGJBFHGM2FDBHQALKTE.jpg&h=2f8b31aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員方震國<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】死因庭證供顯示，案發當晚催淚彈發射的時間及警員何時進入停車場，其中衝鋒隊指揮官與部份隊員所講的記錄，均與直播新聞及停車場閉路電視時間相差數分鐘；此外，不但該隊指揮官稱行動前沒與其他小隊指揮官對錶，多名隊員亦一致指行動前沒有對錶。有隊員昨表示，指揮官沒要求他們即時看錶紀錄每發催淚彈的時間。死因裁判官亦向家屬明言，警方提供的時間「好明顯唔準確」。<br />\n<br />\n事發當晚凌晨發射了七枚催淚彈的衝鋒隊第4小隊、警員嚴卓勳昨供稱，由於他要「集中望住危險點」，而傳令員會負責記錄發射時間，故他僅於發射第一枚催淚彈時有看錶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隊員認有出入不會修正<br />\n<br />\n惟同隊警員方震國指，雖然小隊指揮。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n該隊隊員、女警楊樂欣則表示。。。。。。。。。。。惟即使記錄時間與自己記憶有出入，她亦不會提出修正。<br />\n<br />\n昨散庭前，死因裁判官高偉雄主動問家屬一方需否考慮傳召第4小隊的傳令員出庭，但明言「好明顯警方掌握嘅時間唔正確」，或不需傳召傳令員。家屬一方代表大狀同意，但稱要先索取指示。"},{"pid":"c05c5a465f517bad12f6d856561b9a9813c289f4","tid":2293199,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"終於影到黑暴大頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459f8db43aaca106a8627b406395f27305e64ee0","tid":2293199,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"唔係不準<br />\n<br />\n係做手腳"},{"pid":"c14b28c9cbd4a9b743287d01d5547e62152575ea","tid":2293199,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"大話精！黑警死全家"}]}